id: pm-web-7pxa
title: Deepen pm-web extension command surface (status/stop/doctor) + services-capability evaluation
description: "Add curated pm-extension commands so the pm-web server is fully manageable through pm without breaking the app, Docker image, or existing 'pm web' command. Adds: pm web status (probe /healthz), pm web stop (pidfile-tracked detached stop), pm web doctor (preflight diagnostics). Evaluates the 'services' capability. Introduces a CommandError class (numeric exitCode) for new handlers. Minimal additive server change: /healthz now returns version."
